
This is version 1.2 of finance, a Motif based loan calculator.  Given
a term in YEARS, the PRINCIPAL loan amount, and interest RATE, it computes
the monthly PAYMENT.  Setting the PAYMENT text field recomputes PRINCIPAL.

Finance.ad	Application defaults file.
Imakefile	System independent imake description file.
Finance.ftr	File typing rules file.
README.finance		This file.
finance.man	Manual page (nroff source).
main.c		Calculator source program.


To build and run: 

	xmkmf
	make
	finance

to install:

	su
	make install install.man
